libpaseto
------------------------------------------
libpaseto is a low-level implementation of Platform-Agnostic Security Tokens in
C. It only supports v2 public and private tokens, v1 is not supported. PASETO
Registered Claims are not in the scope of this project but can be built ontop
of libpaseto.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.1.2-1
  libpaseto-devel-1.0-1bl1
  libpaseto0-1.0-1bl1
  libsodium-devel-1.0.18-1
  libsodium23-1.0.18-1
  pkg-config-1.6.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.29-1
  cmake-3.14.5-1
  cygport-0.33.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  ninja-1.9.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/authenticvision/libpaseto

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/authenticvision/libpaseto/archive/1.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libpaseto-1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libpaseto-1.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libpaseto-1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libpaseto-1.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libpaseto0-1.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libpaseto-devel-1.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libpaseto)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libpaseto.README
  /usr/share/doc/libpaseto/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libpaseto/README.md

(libpaseto0)
  /usr/bin/cygpaseto-0.dll

(libpaseto-devel)
  /usr/include/paseto.h
  /usr/lib/libpaseto.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/paseto.pc

------------------

